<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Donate | PubLife</title>

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<style>

* { box-sizing: border-box; }

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
  color: white;
  background: black;
}

/* BACKGROUND */
.bg {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background: url('bar-blur.jpg') center center / cover no-repeat;
  z-index: -3;
}

.overlay {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(0,0,0,0.9));
  z-index: -2;
}

/* CONTENT */
.container {
  max-width: 420px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 100px 20px 40px;
  text-align: center;
}

/* HEADLINE */
h1 {
  font-size: 32px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

/* TEXT */
.text {
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  color: #f4f1ea;
}

/* BUTTONS */
.btn {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  margin: 12px auto;
  padding: 16px;
  font-size: 17px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  text-decoration: none;
  text-align: center;
  font-weight: bold;
}

/* ZEFFY */
.zeffy {
  background: #6c63ff;
  color: white;
}

/* GOFUNDME */
.gfm {
  background: #02a95c;
  color: white;
}

/* VENMO */
.venmo {
  background: #3d95ce;
  color: white;
}

/* BACK LINK */
.back {
  margin-top: 30px;
  display: inline-block;
  color: #b08d57;
  text-decoration: underline;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="bg"></div>
<div class="overlay"></div>

<div class="container">

  <h1>Support PubLife</h1>

  <div class="text">
    We’ve partnered with Zeffy to ensure that <strong>100% of your donation goes directly to helping hospitality workers</strong> facing medical emergencies.
    <br><br>
    Zeffy is a secure, fee-free platform built specifically for nonprofits.
    <br><br>
    For those who prefer, we also offer GoFundMe and Venmo as alternative ways to give.
  </div>

  <a href="https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/donation-form/help-publife-support-hospitality-workers-with-medical-costs" class="btn zeffy">
    Donate with Zeffy (No Fees)
  </a>

  <a href="https://gofund.me/35bd90c1a" class="btn gfm">
    Donate with GoFundMe
  </a>

  <a href="https://venmo.com/YOUR-USERNAME" class="btn venmo">
    Donate with Venmo
  </a>

  <a href="index.html" class="back">← Back to Home</a>

</div>

</body>
</html>
